  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV49">
<l>paṇṭum palapala vīṅkiruḷ kāṇṭumip pāyiruḷpōṟ</l>
<l>kaṇṭu maṟivatuṅ kēṭpatum yāmilaṅ kāḷavaṇṇa</l>
<l>vaṇṭuṇ ṭuḻāypperu māṉmatu cūtaṉaṉ tāmōtara</l>
<l>ṉuṇṭu mumiḻntuṅ kaṭāyamaṇ ṇēraṉṉa voṇṇutalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Formerly we would have seen many many swelling darknesses. [Something] like this spreading darkness,</l>
<l>although we see [it], is neither known nor heard of by us, you with bright forehead,</l>
<l>like the fineness of the earth eaten, spit out [and] commanded by the great lord</l>
<l>with Tulsi eaten by bees of black colour, by Matucūtaṉaṉ, by Tāmōtaraṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
